gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Bucks 131, Wizards 128
gameRecap.excerpt: The Bucks defeated the Wizards, 131-128. Brook Lopez led the Bucks with a career-high tying 39 points (4-7 3PT, 14-17 overall) as Giannis Antetokounmpo (31 points, nine rebounds, three assists) and Damian Lillard (31 points, 10 assists, seven rebounds) recorded 30-point games as well. Jordan Poole led the Wizards with 26 points, seven assists, and five rebounds while Kyle Kuzma added 22 points. The Bucks move to 3-0 in East B play and 11-5 on the year as the Wizards move to 2-13 on the year and 0-4 in IST play.
